<title>ṣʿb ktyr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ṣʿb ktyr ạ̉bʿd yạ gẖạly ṣʿb ktyr ạ̉nsạk yạ
 fạdy
 dy mḥbtk fy ʿrwqy sạryẗ mtạ̉ṣlẗ
 wrḥmtk jwạya sạknẗ mtfsrẗ
 wḥty̱ lw ṣbḥt ẓrwfy mtkdrẗ
 ạ̉nạ nfsy msẖfyẗ bdmk mtḥrrẗ
 lạ lạ msẖ hạnsạk lạ dạ ạ̉nạ ʿmry mʿạk
 qlby ạ̉syr ḥbk yạ jạhy sẖrfy kbyr ạ̹nk ạ̹lhy
 ạ̉nạ ḥr fyk wʿbd lyk brgẖbty
 wmạ dạm wrạk hạwṣl mʿạk lfrḥty
 wḥty̱ lw yqsy̱ ạlzmạn ạ̉nạ lyk hạʿysẖ</lyrics>
</song>